<div style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)">
<div class="hero">
  <div>
    <div class="hero-eye">PRIVACY MIDDLEWARE FOR AGENTIC AI</div>
    <h1>Privacy Guard<br>for <span>Agentic AI</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Automatically detects, redacts, or pseudonymizes personal data before it reaches an LLM or gets stored in memory. Complete compliance mapping, prompt injection protection, and re-identification risk scoring — all in one middleware.</p>
    <div class="hf-row">
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:var(--accent)"></span>PII Detection</div>
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:var(--teal)"></span>Policy Engine</div>
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:#f687b3"></span>Compliance Mapper</div>
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:var(--danger)"></span>Injection Shield</div>
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:var(--warn)"></span>Re-ID Scorer</div>
      <div class="hf"><span class="hf-dot" style="background:var(--success)"></span>Audit Trail</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#demo"><button class="btn-primary">▶ Try Live Demo</button></a>
      <a href="#proof"><button class="btn-sec">View Proof Report</button></a>
