<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-val">23/23</div><div class="sb-lbl">TESTS PASSING</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-val">7</div><div class="sb-lbl">PII TYPES DETECTED</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-val">14</div><div class="sb-lbl">INJECTION PATTERNS</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-val">4</div><div class="sb-lbl">LAWS COVERED</div></div>
  <div class="sb-item"><div class="sb-val">6</div><div class="sb-lbl">API ENDPOINTS</div></div>
</div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="sec-eye">CAPABILITIES</div>
  <div class="sec-title">What PII-Safe does</div>
  <div class="sec-sub">Six core engines working together to protect every piece of data through the entire pipeline</div>
  <div class="feats">
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">01</div><div class="fc-ico">🔍</div><div class="fc-name">PII Detection</div><div class="fc-desc">Schema-aware detection across 7 entity types using regex patterns with confidence scoring and privacy risk assessment.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">email, IP, SSN, credit card</div><div class="fcc">phone, API key, username</div><div class="fcc">Confidence scoring per match</div></div></div>
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">02</div><div class="fc-ico">📋</div><div class="fc-name">Policy Engine</div><div class="fc-desc">YAML policy-as-code evaluates each request against declarative rules and returns a clear decision.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">allow / redact / pseudonymize / block</div><div class="fcc">Hot-reload without restart</div><div class="fcc">Context-aware rule matching</div></div></div>
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">03</div><div class="fc-ico">⚖️</div><div class="fc-name">Compliance Mapper</div><div class="fc-desc">Maps detected PII to exact legal articles with severity scoring across 4 major privacy frameworks.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">GDPR Article 17, Recital 30</div><div class="fcc">HIPAA 45 CFR 164.514(b)</div><div class="fcc">CCPA §1798.105, PCI-DSS R3</div></div></div>
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">04</div><div class="fc-ico">🛡️</div><div class="fc-name">Injection Shield</div><div class="fc-desc">Detects 14 prompt injection attack patterns hidden inside data before they reach the LLM.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">Instruction overrides</div><div class="fcc">Persona hijacks, role spoofing</div><div class="fcc">Encoded payloads, prompt leaks</div></div></div>
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">05</div><div class="fc-ico">📊</div><div class="fc-name">Re-ID Risk Scorer</div><div class="fc-desc">Calculates residual re-identification risk from field combinations even after partial redaction.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">Based on Sweeney research</div><div class="fcc">Combination risk detection</div><div class="fcc">Critical / High / Medium / Low</div></div></div>
    <div class="fc"><div class="fc-num">06</div><div class="fc-ico">📝</div><div class="fc-name">Audit Trail</div><div class="fc-desc">Every transformation logged with original value, replacement token, action type, and scope ID.</div><div class="fc-check"><div class="fcc">Secure token mapping</div><div class="fcc">Authorized re-identification</div><div class="fcc">Scope-consistent pseudonyms</div></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

